@startuml 02-software
title ソフトウェア構成図 (Bootstrap Step 1: Hello UF2)

skinparam defaultFontName "Noto Sans CJK JP"
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam package {
  BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
  BorderColor #555
}
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #EEF6FF
  BorderColor #336699
}
skinparam artifact {
  BackgroundColor #FFF6E0
  BorderColor #B58A00
}

package "ホスト PC (Linux / WSL2)" as PC {
  component "scripts/build-pico.sh" as Build
  artifact  "firmware.uf2" as UF2
  component "BOOTSEL マウント\n(/media/RPI-RP2)" as Mount
  component "minicom / screen\n@ /dev/ttyACM0 115200" as Term

  Build -down-> UF2
  UF2 -down-> Mount : D&D
}

package "Pico 2 ファームウェア (RP2350)" as Pico {
  component "main.cpp\n(printf ループ)" as App
  component "Pico SDK\n(stdlib / stdio_usb)" as SDK
  component "TinyUSB CDC" as CDC
  component "ROM Bootloader\n(BOOTSEL → MSC)" as Boot

  App  -down-> SDK   : printf
  SDK  -down-> CDC   : stdio_usb
}

Mount ..[#aa3333]..> Boot : UF2 を MSC 書き込み
Boot  ..[#aa3333]..> App  : フラッシュ後\n再起動 → main()
CDC   .[#cc6600].> Term  : "Hello, world!\\n"\n(1 秒周期)

note bottom of PC
  ビルドは Pico SDK + arm-none-eabi-gcc。
  生成は CMake (Ninja) で firmware/build/ 以下に出力。
end note

note bottom of Pico
  この段階では Verilog / Verilator 由来の
  C++ は未リンク。flash / SRAM のベースラインを計測する。
end note

@enduml
